{"tid":2394792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局要求學校成立國家安全教育小組定期交報告","createTime":"2021-02-04T12:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T12:39:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"695480e9be170ac503ca37b38b012cb6a732434d","tid":2394792,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"教育局要求學校成立國家安全教育小組，由校內管理層領導，需定期向教育局匯報進展和提交工作報告，要求校方勸止校內政治活動，若教師宣揚個人政治立場，屬違反專業操守。<br />\n<br />\n教育局要求學校成立國家安全教育小組，按校本需要擬定計劃，國際學校及私立中小學及幼稚園除外。<br />\n<br />\n維護國家安全及國家安全教育工作小組成員，需要由校監或校長、學校各科及小組組成，亦可加入社工或教育心理學家等。<br />\n<br />\n小組負責促進各級人員了解香港國安法，策劃和統籌有關安排，協調各科落實措施，制定應變措施，防止政治活動入侵校園，需要定期向辦學團體及教育局匯報工作進展及提交年度報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=422955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422955&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRL9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=93501070\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422955&h=926b035c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=422955</a>"},{"pid":"4b2f0393205346f1d1a5c4b7bac35a76e13e1351","tid":2394792,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d2e69459d2529c1e4ed1dc14882002a38d7c09","tid":2394792,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822a5d197dac51350db8a0c551c3aae54e6700d8","tid":2394792,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:35:03.000Z","msg":"講到教育局唔係喺學校搞政治活動咁"},{"pid":"e35a4e6a0c392bcdf215509c4cec09387c9f341b","tid":2394792,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:39:44.000Z","msg":"學校幫紫荊黨拉票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}